Forms of [[Introverted Judgement]]:

* [[Introverted Thinking]]
* [[Introverted Feeling]]

@@i2

In [[Lenore]]'s view, [[Extraverted Perception]] and [[Introverted Judgement]] are opposed enough to cause some internal conflict, but compatible enough that they generate synergy and intelligent adaptation and individuation pretty quickly and easily.
